## 4. Entry Points

| Component | How It Starts |
|---|---|
| **Backend (default)** | `python -m automation.main` → `main()` → `chat.start_chat()` — starts REPL + API server on port 5001 |
| **Backend (server only)** | `python -m automation.main --server` → `server.run_server()` |
| **Backend (single task)** | `python -m automation.main --task "Go to google.com"` → `main_async()` |
| **Backend (CSV workflow)** | `python -m automation.main --workflow file.csv` → loads CSV → LLM → runner |
| **Extension** | `manifest.json` → `background.js` (service worker) + `content.js` (injected into all pages) |
| **Website** | `npm run dev` in `website/` → Next.js dev server (port 3000) |
| **Installer** | `pip install autopattern-install && autopattern-install` → installs uv → installs autopattern |

