## 8. External Dependencies

| Dependency | Type | What It Does |
|---|---|---|
| **Google Gemini API** | REST API (via `langchain-google-genai` + `google-genai`) | Powers all LLM calls — workflow analysis, task description, agent reasoning |
| **Playwright CDN** | Binary download | Downloads Chromium for Testing (~250MB) on first run |
| **IndexedDB** (browser-local) | Client-side DB | Extension stores all workflow recordings locally in the browser |
| **No external database** | — | No Postgres, Redis, SQLite, or any server-side persistence |
| **No authentication** | — | API server is wide open on `0.0.0.0:5001` with `allow_origins=["*"]` |

